## Context Files

The `context/` directory contains structured project management files:

- `context/OWNER.md` — Profile of the project owner (shared across projects)
- `context/DECISIONS.md` — Decision log (inverse chronological)
- `context/BACKLOG.md` — Task registry with unique IDs (BACK-NNN)
- `context/PROJECTS.md` — Project registry with unique IDs (PROJ-NNN)
- `context/STANDUPS.md` — Daily standup template and log
- `context/PRD.md` — Product requirements document
- `context/work-instructions/GENERAL.md` — General rules for AI agents
- `context/work-instructions/DEVELOPMENT.md` — Development-specific rules
- `context/work-instructions/TEAM.md` — Team collaboration rules
- `context/project-notes/` — Deep research on specific topics
- `context/ideas/` — Future direction research
